  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Holiday Club Spa Hotel is on a half board basis for guests staying within the hotel, this includes breakfast and dinner. For guests staying within the apartments, these are on a self catering board basis - meals are not included. There is an option to pre-book half board at the <a data-udi="umb://document/c661c78119c84b88b761eef9614441f2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c661c78119c84b88b761eef9614441f2}" title="Holiday Club Spa Hotel">Holiday Club Spa</a>, which includes breakfast and dinner. </p>
<p>Breakfast is buffet style often including a continental offering of pastries, bread, fresh fruit, yogurt and daily hot options. Open between 7am-10am.</p>
<p>Dinner is a three-course buffet served from 5pm-8pm or you can receive an €11 credit towards the à la carte menu at Restaurant Rakka, when having a three-course meal.</p>
<p>Festive buffet dinners are included on Christmas Eve and New Year's Eve.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
