  <description><![CDATA[<p>Make the most of your Lapland holiday and stay in the Holiday Club Spa Hotel in <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselk<span>ä</span></a>. The popular spa hotel offers a high standard of accommodation and an impressive range of facilities, including a fabulous indoor pool complex.</p>
<h2>Ideal location </h2>
<p>Everything you need for your winter break is only a short walk away, located at the top end of <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselk<span>ä</span>,</a> you'll have easy access to a range of scenic routes - perfect for hiking or cross country skiing,  bars and restaurants and excursions. The bus stop is just outside the hotel too, so heading to the ski slopes is really easy as well.</p>
<h2>Wellness facilities </h2>
<p>The main draw of the hotel is its spa and leisure facilities, featuring an indoor swimming pool with waterslides and spa area for the adults. The children can have fun racing down the waterslides, while the adults can unwind and rest in the Finnish sauna. After a day spent adventuring in <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselk<span>ä</span></a>, the whole family can warm up and rest in the jacuzzi. <span> Indulge yourself with a treatment from the spa menu for the ultimate treat.</span></p>
<h2>Warm and modern</h2>
<p><span>The rooms are comfortable, and have the amenities needed for a relaxing stay in Lapland including a TV, drying cabinet or heated towel rail, a kettle and a hairdryer. </span><span>The lounge features an open fireplace, making it the ideal location for a digestif at the end of the day. The dining area is contemporary and modern, all meals are served buffet style - each day there is a choice of menu often featuring a choice of Lappish and international dishes. Meal times are flexible, so you can choose a time that suits you.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><span><em>This hotel </em></span><em>can also be booked as part of our '<a data-udi="umb://document/7d16724b0f3b4033952b780a65425621" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d16724b0f3b4033952b780a65425621}" title="Muotka 2-Centre Adventure">Muotka 2-Centre Adventure</a>'.</em></p>]]></description>
