  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms </strong>are around 22m<sup>2  </sup>and sleeps two to four people with two twin beds and sofa, which can be turned into a double sofa bed for full occupancy. </p>
<p><strong>Economy Twin Rooms </strong>are around 18<span>m</span><sup>2  </sup>and are available for single use. Available at no supplement for the first one single room booked on each arrival date. A supplement applies to additional single occupancy rooms.</p>
